file.name: snake-case.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Snake case example
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /v1/test:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
components:
  schemas:
    'not a valid identifier':
      type: number
    rubiks_cube_face:
      enum: [f, r, u, l, b, d]
    rubiks_cube_step:
      type: object
      additionalProperties: false
      properties:
        face:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/rubiks_cube_face'
        turns:
          enum: [-1, 1, 2]
      required:
        - face
        - turns
    rubiks_cube_algorithm:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/rubiks_cube_step'
